text: i think this is ready for deeper feedback

there are a few things you should notice:
 - if you click on a deck in recent decks, it now takes you to a deck preview instead of taking you away from edhrec. Here it has a list of similar decks + recommendations built in
 - There is a new item under the commander “List of decks” which has a table in it. Note that it’ll filter down if you go pick the theme, and you can sort by budget etc.
overall idea is making it easier to browse actual decklists on edhrec
